[Preparing Data] Add MerchantUrl 10305919, Package 10306389 and OneTime PricePoint 10313345

[Preparing Data] Create EU merchant with ID 10259884
[Preparing Data] Add MerchantUrl 10305920, Package 10306390 and Recurring PricePoint 10313346

[SignupPayPage] Selecting JPY currency
[SignupPayPage] Enabling CrossSell-1 checkbox
[SignupPayPage] Submitting the page
[SignupPayPage] Signup transaction is created (ID 226298703)
